    44вҶ’	Use-cases:
    45вҶ’	1. Parse JSON via the [`bourne` package](https://github.com/hapijs/bourne) to protect from prototype pollution.
    46вҶ’	2. Parse JSON with [`reviver` option of `JSON.parse()`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/JSON/parse).
    47вҶ’
    48вҶ’	@default JSON.parse()
    49вҶ’
    50вҶ’	@example
    51вҶ’	```
    52вҶ’	import ky from 'ky';
    53вҶ’	import bourne from '@hapijs/bourne';
    54вҶ’
    55вҶ’	const json = await ky('https://example.com', {
